premise_source_doc_sentence: A member of the Gyllenhaal family and the son of director Stephen Gyllenhaal and screenwriter Naomi Foner , Gyllenhaal began acting as a child with a screen debut in City Slickers  (  1991  )  , followed by roles in A Dangerous Woman  (  1993  )  and Homegrown  (  1998  )  .
Nine Stories Productions is a New-York based film , theater and television production company founded by Jake Gyllenhaal and Riva Marker in 2015 .
